OL,3,CWhy Wales and Ireland will wear red
OL,4,Cand green for the final time when they
OL,5,Cplay
OL,7,FIreland and Wales will play each other
OL,8,Fin their traditional plain green and
OL,9,Fred shirts for the final time during
OL,10,Ftheir game this weekend (Saturday, 24
OL,11,FFebruary).
OL,13,FThe green-red combination can make it
OL,14,Fdifficult for people who are colour-
OL,15,Fblind to tell the difference between
OL,16,Fthe teams.
OL,18,FAround one in 12 men suffer from
OL,19,Fcolour vision deficiency (CVD) and one
OL,20,Fin 200 women.
