OL,3,CWhy Wales and Ireland will wear red
OL,4,Cand green for the final time when they
OL,5,Cplay
OL,7,FWorld Rugby regulations will come into
OL,8,Fforce from January next year to try to
OL,9,Fmake it easier for people with CVD to
OL,10,Fwatch games.
OL,12,FThose regulations will be adopted by
OL,13,Fthe Six Nations, and all teams will
OL,14,Fneed to avoid kit clashes that could
OL,15,Fnegatively impact spectators and
OL,16,Ftelevision viewers suffering from CVD.
