OL,3,CWhy Wales and Ireland will wear red
OL,4,Cand green for the final time when they
OL,5,Cplay
OL,7,FSix Nations guidance will see visiting
OL,8,Fteams asked to wear change kits where
OL,9,Fa colour match has been identified,
OL,10,Fmeaning Ireland would wear a change
OL,11,Fstrip in Cardiff next year.
OL,13,FWales' current change strip is black,
OL,14,Fwhich wouldn't help much, as colours
OL,15,Flike red and green can look too
OL,16,Fsimilar to this for someone with CVD.
