OL,3,CWhy Wales and Ireland will wear red
OL,4,Cand green for the final time when they
OL,5,Cplay
OL,7,FWelsh Rugby Union chief executive Abi
OL,8,FTierney said: "Kit colour clashes do
OL,9,Fchange the way you watch a game, and I
OL,10,Fhave absolute empathy with those whose
OL,11,Fenjoyment is affected as a result.
OL,13,F"Our current alternate kit is black,
OL,14,Fand we have used green in the recent
OL,15,Fpast. Neither of these examples
OL,16,Fparticularly help with this issue, and
OL,17,Fadditionally, the colour red in Wales
OL,18,Fis not just traditional, but a part of
OL,19,Four culture.
