OL,3,CWhy Wales and Ireland will wear red
OL,4,Cand green for the final time when they
OL,5,Cplay
OL,7,F"But there are other ways to work
OL,8,Faround the issues, and kits with
OL,9,Fsignificantly different designs can
OL,10,Fhelp avoid the problem too.
OL,12,F"We need to think laterally about how
OL,13,Fwe can overcome the issue ahead of
OL,14,Fnext year, perhaps not just with more
OL,15,Finventive use of colours, but in our
OL,16,Fkit designs too.
