OL,3,CWhy Wales and Ireland will wear red
OL,4,Cand green for the final time when they
OL,5,Cplay
OL,7,F"If one team is in checks and the
OL,8,Fother is in stripes, for example, then
OL,9,Fcolours become pretty irrelevant, but
OL,10,Fwe are thinking hard about a solution
OL,11,Fthat works for everyone.
OL,13,F"We recognise that this is a serious
OL,14,Fissue for many fans, and we are taking
OL,15,Fit very seriously ourselves.
OL,17,F"It is regrettable that we haven't
OL,18,Freached a resolution to suit all this
OL,19,Fseason, but I can confirm we are fully
OL,20,Fcommitted to correcting that in the
OL,21,Fnext kit cycle."
